{"tid":1122263,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"押注獨角獸勁賺　李嘉誠基金會累捐逾300億","createTime":"2019-04-24T00:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T11:56:00.000Z","uid":81228,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd007102fd546a33da8b15ef75bacfa97dfbebc9","tid":1122263,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T00:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/04/23/2115948_02f118d5f1429f1f1c85d5de3a5b2be5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F04%2F23%2F2115948_02f118d5f1429f1f1c85d5de3a5b2be5.jpg&h=767b392a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nZoom創辦人袁征（左）去年在加州與李嘉誠見面。<br />\n<br />\n長和（00001）創辦人李嘉誠旗下維港投資（Horizons Ventures）有份押注的「獨角獸」Zoom自上周在美國掛牌，股價連日暴漲近七成，再次展示李嘉誠眼光精準，而背後大贏家其實也包括普羅大眾，皆因李嘉誠在Zoom等科企方面的投資收益均全數用於慈善。據了解，李嘉誠基金會至今累計捐款超過300 ...<br />\n（節錄）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/finnews/article/2115948/%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E7%8D%A8%E8%A7%92%E7%8D%B8%E5%8B%81%E8%B3%BA+%E6%9D%8E%E5%98%89%E8%AA%A0%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E6%9C%83%E7%B4%AF%E6%8D%90%E9%80%BE300%E5%84%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Fdailynews%2Ffinnews%2Farticle%2F2115948%2F%25E6%258A%25BC%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E7%258D%25A8%25E8%25A7%2592%25E7%258D%25B8%25E5%258B%2581%25E8%25B3%25BA%2B%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%2598%2589%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E6%258D%2590%25E9%2580%25BE300%25E5%2584%2584&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubC%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=4141b1d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/finnews/article/2115948/%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8%E7%8D%A8%E8%A7%92%E7%8D%B8%E5%8B%81%E8%B3%BA+%E6%9D%8E%E5%98%89%E8%AA%A0%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E6%9C%83%E7%B4%AF%E6%8D%90%E9%80%BE300%E5%84%84</a>"},{"pid":"5d33a3daa2709c38d2129d533ec613a76a9e6515","tid":1122263,"uid":243380,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T00:56:01.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠投資左咁多venture中一個有幾奇<img src=\"